696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a>宣布了他们的新专辑《Midas》，并分享了他们的重磅新单曲《July》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/wunderhorse-interview-jacob-slater-cub-album-fontaines-dc-radar-3323294">Wunderhorse：由朋克转型的美国作曲家，深受 Fontaines DC 喜爱</a></strong></li></ul><p>《Midas》将于 8 月 30 日通过 Communion 发布，可<a href="https://wunderhorseband.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>。该唱片将作为乐队 2022 年突破性首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/wunderhorse-cub-review-jacob-slater-radar-3319474">Cub</a> 》的后续作品。该歌曲是在明尼苏达州的 Pachyderm Studio（ <a href="/artists/Nirvana">Nirvana</a>的“In Utero”和<a href="/artists/PJ-Harvey">PJ Harvey</a>的“Rid Of Me”的诞生地）与制作人 Craig Silvey（<a href="/artists/The-Rolling-Stones">滚石乐队</a>、<a href="/artists/The-National">国家乐队</a>）录制的。</p><p>在新闻稿中谈到《Midas》的创作时，主唱兼吉他手雅各布·斯莱特 (Jacob Slater) 表示：“当我们第一次进入录音室制作这张唱片时，我们唯一确定的是我们希望它听起来如何；非常不完美，非常生动，非常原始；没有多余的装饰。我们希望它听起来就像你的脸压在放大器上，就像你被锁在低音鼓里一样。” </p><figure id="attachment_3757057" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3757057" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3757057" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Wunderhorse-Midas-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Wunderhorse &#39;Midas&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Wunderhorse-Midas-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Wunderhorse-Midas-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Wunderhorse-Midas-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Wunderhorse-Midas-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Wunderhorse-Midas-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Wunderhorse-Midas-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Wunderhorse-Midas-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3757057" class="wp-caption-text"> Wunderhorse &#39;Midas&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><strong>Wunderhorse &#39;Midas&#39; 曲目列表是：</strong></p><p> <strong>1.“迈达斯”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“雨”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“艾米丽”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“银”</strong><br /> <strong>5.《亚利桑那》</strong><br /> <strong>6.《超人》</strong><br /> <strong>7.“七月”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“大教堂”</strong><br /> <strong>9.“女孩”</strong><br /> <strong>10.“飞机”</strong></p><p>随着他们的第二张录音室专辑的发布，Wunderhorse 还分享了他们令人难以忘怀的歌曲“July”。开场时，斯莱特唱着<em>“我的头着火了/我缺氧了/电话不响/沉默/沉默”，</em>表达了他的沮丧。这首单曲充满了坚韧的吉他和雷鸣般的鼓声。</p><p>朱莉的随行视觉师看到各种玩具和物品，如巨魔娃娃、一套嵌套娃娃、玩具马、纸面具、玩具旋转木马和一个小剧院舞台，被喷灯点燃并以慢动作点燃。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Wunderhorse - 七月（视觉效果）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/haBa7gplaMs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C6O0LmdMohq/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; borde